KY93Bh5U7sddVPuU7J_nMo6DRFUyqy20Pf45IrCClV471Yj3MLOvvtqcw5MM2YOq1Gpj-RStRvdLW0NfI0H2DQbnAbkQeM1i9zDw_9ZuX4C7_wgTk6HI1n93KDnJ5aq-ev_zE1K_Vnalvb9s3tlHuxmuDv3lC056GKXBSPPAgsPp3j4e0vjhx_ROs4VUbd6QaoFKzAwlblQphwIx0VcmKcc6xnDKWXFhupw9A-XLKPWMvTF4KFe9QHCm6yNZnr__apfLeikh1iiJss7sa5M6nMEFW6i3tJJOA8YuzdIJUWDtMSp4hYdAuugk%26__tn__%3DEEHH-R&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=1d8f1959\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/photos/a.122771689139239/276881257061614/?type=3&amp;eid=ARCiWSSDuxAXtbrbpel_ljzSAkn2CB0Gy5nhG7qnqHz-5qIRNYHK-LhjkSyTM1YUyp--tUz73VO_Oirf&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARBzPk4uXo5PnbIbzH9-UzRKzzmJ3JHKY93Bh5U7sddVPuU7J_nMo6DRFUyqy20Pf45IrCClV471Yj3MLOvvtqcw5MM2YOq1Gpj-RStRvdLW0NfI0H2DQbnAbkQeM1i9zDw_9ZuX4C7_wgTk6HI1n93KDnJ5aq-ev_zE1K_Vnalvb9s3tlHuxmuDv3lC056GKXBSPPAgsPp3j4e0vjhx_ROs4VUbd6QaoFKzAwlblQphwIx0VcmKcc6xnDKWXFhupw9A-XLKPWMvTF4KFe9QHCm6yNZnr__apfLeikh1iiJss7sa5M6nMEFW6i3tJJOA8YuzdIJUWDtMSp4hYdAuugk&amp;__tn__=EEHH-R</a><br />\n本台收到消息，拔萃男書院校方將向學生發通告，因附屬小學小三學生家長確診武肺，小學部及中學部明起開始停課，直至另行通知，明日起將重新採用視像教學。<br />\n<br />\n本港爆發第三波武漢肺炎疫情，單在今日就出現14宗確診個案，連同拔萃附小在內，現時至少有7間學校，有學生或家長確診或成密切接觸者因而宣佈要即時停課。香港演藝學院亦出現確診個案，今日亦一同緊急停課。另外，沙田區今日亦出現至少3宗確診個案，不排除有社區爆發風險。<br />\n<br />\n隨著武肺第三波疫情疑似爆發，不少議員已經要求教育局宣布提早放暑假，以減低進一步爆發的風險。<br />\n<br />\n文/J<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #加山傳播 #DBChannel #武漢肺炎 #停課了 #放暑假了"},{"pid":"e6ff7bb12602073aaa128fe30552b50c7dada4f4","tid":2098614,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"YES!!!!!!!!!"}]}